	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>I decided to do the Trueshot quest but ran into a problem.&nbsp;&nbsp;I gave the laterns to Jyle Windshot he just kept them and told me I wasn't an enemy of Faydark Champions but I wasn't a friend either.  I conned indifferent to him.  I did some checking and found I could raise my faction with them by doing a muffin quest that was in West Freeport.  Pinia Brownloe is by the Theatre in the same zone so I bought 10 stacks of muffins and gave them in groups of 4 to Panda Flintside.  He is the dwarf at the end of the hall that Jyle room is at.  4 or 5 stacks would have been enough but I gave all of them to him anyway and went from indifferent to adminable in less than 30 minutes.<br><br>Feedwin Kornfeet <br>Ranger of the 24th season<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
