	   <a name=104734569541124></a>
	   <form action=http://www1.allakhazam.com/perl/strategy/mrate.pl name=f104734569541124><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=item.html?item=2672&mid=104734569541124>RE: Improving faction for Faydark Champions</a> <a id=fs8 href=item.html?item=2672&mid=104734569541124#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=181619><span id= >animekenji</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>282 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Mon, Mar 10th 8:55 PM 2003</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[2.71]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Kill Crushbone orcs until you can't stand the sight of their ugly blue faces and then kill about a hundred more for good measure. You'll have more than enough faction to do this quest, plus the dwarves will love you, besides. Currently my faction with Crushbone Orcs can't possibly be any worse while my Stormguard faction can't get any better. I think Stormguard faction increases more than elf factions because even though I have the best possible faction in Kaladim, my elf factions still are not maxed and I'm an elf, myself. Don't ask me how that worked out. BTW, I got to master in fletching before attempting my Trueshot and failed. :( Faced with the prospect of running all over Norrath and wasting much time gathering components for another try, (I got killed by wandering pirates 4 times while buying kiola nuts on sister isle, I was only level 17 then) I broke down and bought one for 140PP in bazaar and don't regret it a bit. Sometimes you get lucky and see them as low as 100 but 150-200 seems to be the norm with only a few people trying to get more than that. Heck, I even saw a Raincaller for 500 once. All the charges were gone, but for the ratio and the range with the buffs that was still a steal.<br><br><br>How long ago did you do the muffin quest?? That was removed at the same time as the cleansing of the karanas GM event and that was like 1.5-2 years ago or more if I remember correctly.<br>&nbsp;<br>If you were me and I were you, would we still be friends?</td></tr>
