	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Pandos is still up and taking muffins on Povar. Faction adjustments are showing, though I handed muffins to him unstacked since one patch reportedly removed the stacking effect. Took 1,500 to get from threateningly to apprehensive.<br>On the other hand, it took about 7 stacks of Tumpy Tonics for the same Dark Elf rogue of Bristlebane to get to warmly and kindly in North Freeport.<br>Pandos is an intensive quest, but worth it if you have the time and need the faction. Much faster than killing orcs.<br>&nbsp;<br>Nightseer,<br>Rogue of Povar<br>GL of 1,000 Alts<br>Phoenix Ascendent</td></tr>
