	   <tr><td colspan=2>A few more notes,<br>Micro Servos drop off the runaway clockworks (the spiders, not the gnome shaped clockworks).<br>About every 4 lanterns you give Jyle Windshots, you'll get a trent heart (I believe thats the name) which is used in another quest somewhere.<br>You can make tumpy tonics yourself with brewing. You need to combine one kiola nut and a water flask in a brewing barrel. It trivials at 135.<br>I believe the Trueshot trivials at 235. So with a fletching of 1 you have a 5% chance of succeeding, or so says varent.<br>&nbsp;<br>Type:EKA 1% fall into this type<br>Explorer: 80% Killer: 46%<br>Achiever:40%&nbsp;&nbsp;Socializer:33%</td></tr>
